  "summary": "Apache Tomcat: Cloud membership for clustering component exposed the Kubernetes bearer token",
  "details": "Insertion of Sensitive Information into Log File vulnerability in the cloud membership for clustering component of Apache Tomcat exposed the Kubernetes bearer token.\n\nThis issue affects Apache Tomcat: from 11.0.0 through 11.0.20, from 10.1.0 through 10.1.53, from 9.0.13 through 9.0.116.\n\nUsers are recommended to upgrade to version 11.0.21, 10.1.54 or 9.0.117, which fix the issue.",
